'''[[optical]] [[flat]]'''
#{{optics}} a disk of high-quality [[quartz]] [[glass]] having at least one side [[ground]] and [[polished]] with a [[deviation]] in [[flatness]] less than 50 [[nanometer]]s all over, and a [[surface quality]] of 5 [[microfinish]] or less; used, in an [[interferometer]], to measure the flatness of other surfaces